    "description": "“开局一把剑，装备全靠砍！”<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >惊险刺激的战斗</h2>《流浪荒岛》中，有着强大的boss，危险的地牢，和不同岛屿生物群系中不断生成的怪物。<br>你可以搭配武器和装备，解锁强力的技能，砍杀、格挡、翻滚，消灭这些怪物存活下去吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/1f2076bf159c1d56f2a45b3e9d0ee5d5.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典沙盒生存玩法</h2>种田钓鱼，砍树挖矿，建造小屋，这些统统不能少。<br>不过，在这里搞破坏不需要镐子和斧头，一把铁剑足以。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/4d41a8d420765f3cab2b08c7180d0ccb.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁和发展科技</h2>科技改变生活，利用这些科技，你可以升级自己的家园。扩大照明、快速浇水、资源再生...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/b118e289a9e8acd33cd6514aa2a76572.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索小岛，拜访npc</h2>并非所有海岛上都荒芜人烟，有些岛也居住者居民！和居民们打好交道，与他们交易商品。<br>每个小岛都有着独特的生物和资源等待你的探索。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.poster.avif?t=1719341682\" width=500 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.webm?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2241250/extras/92a1b496bd84437d277e10f90a6d9967.mp4?t=1719341682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
